安东尼霍普金斯的家在洛杉矶野火中被毁https://www.nme.com/news/film/anthony-hopkins-home-destroyed-la-wildfires-3827793?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=anthony-hopkins-home-destroyed-la-wildfiresVictoria Luxford Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:19:06 +0000 Film NewsNewsOscars https://www.nme.com/?p=3827793 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安东尼·霍普金斯" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位奥斯卡奖得主自 2019 年起就住在那里</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/anthony-hopkins-home-destroyed-la-wildfires-3827793">安东尼·霍普金斯 (Anthony Hopkins) 的住宅在洛杉矶山火中被毁</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安东尼·霍普金斯" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Anthony-Hopkins-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>好莱坞传奇人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anthony-hopkins">安东尼·霍普金斯爵士</a>是最近在洛杉矶发生的野火中失去家园的人。</p><p> <a href="https://www.tmz.com/2025/01/09/anthony-hopkins-home-destroyed-in-palisades-wildfire/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>TMZ</em></a>报道称，这位演员位于太平洋帕利塞兹的房子被大火完全烧毁，尽管这位演员当时在英国，不需要撤离。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/thor-love-and-thunder-review-3261413">《雷神：爱与雷霆》评论：漫威迄今为止最金属的电影</a></li></ul><p>全市五场不同的火灾已烧毁超过 36,000 英亩土地，据报道已造成 10 人死亡，超过 130,000 人已撤离。这场火灾已成为该市历史上最具破坏性的火灾，官员警告说，大风可能会进一步助长火势。</p><p>霍普金斯因在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/silence-of-the-lambs"><em>《沉默的羔羊》</em></a>和《<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/thor"><em>雷神》</em></a>电影中扮演的角色而闻名，他于 2019 年购买了这处房产，一年前，他在马里布的家险些错过了该地区的一场野火。他在英国的住所也于2000年失火。</p><p>这位两届<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡</a>奖得主与许多好莱坞名人一起证实他们的家园被毁。喜剧演员比利·克里斯托和电视名人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paris-hilton">帕丽斯·希尔顿</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/paris-hilton-and-billy-crystal-among-hollywood-stars-to-lose-homes-in-la-wildfires-3827526">都发表声明讨论他们的损失</a>，而老牌明星詹姆斯·伍兹<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/james-woods-breaks-down-in-tears-after-house-destroyed-by-wildfires-3827444">在接受电视采访时谈到他的家时泪流满面</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3827798" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827798" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827798" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827798" class="wp-caption-text">洛杉矶日落大道的野火（图片来源：Apu Gomes/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>因电视剧<em>《英雄》</em>和电影<em>《我们这一天</em>》而闻名的演员米洛·文蒂米利亚<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/heroes-star-milo-ventimiglia-chokes-up-after-watching-house-burn-down-in-la-wildfires-your-heart-just-breaks-3827763">在描述失去家园时也变得情绪激动</a>。 “它很快就会击中你，”他说。 “你开始思考房子不同部分的所有记忆等等。然后你看到邻居的房子和周围的一切，你的心都碎了”。</p><p>霍普金斯于 12 月 31 日迎来 87 岁生日，他去年透露，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/anthony-hopkins-is-working-on-an-autobiography-i-do-have-quite-a-memory-3574662">计划写一本自传</a>，并与伴侣斯特拉·霍普金斯 (Stella Hopkins) 一起制作一部关于他生活的纪录片。他最近还出演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guy-ritchie">盖·里奇的</a>新电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/anthony-hopkins-to-star-in-new-guy-ritchie-film-wife-dog-3812116"><em>《妻子与狗》</em></a> <em>。</em></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/anthony-hopkins-home-destroyed-la-wildfires-3827793">安东尼·霍普金斯 (Anthony Hopkins) 的住宅在洛杉矶山火中被毁</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Manic Street Preachers 在新单曲《People Ruin Paintings》中探索“真理的毁灭” https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-explore-destruction-of-truth-on-new-single-people-ruin-paintings-3827789?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=躁狂街头传教士探索新单身人士废墟绘画上的真相破坏Damian JonesFri, 10 Jan 2025 10:09:03 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3827789 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="躁狂街传教士的詹姆斯·迪恩·布拉德菲尔德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌取自他们即将发行的专辑“批判性思维”</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-explore-destruction-of-truth-on-new-single-people-ruin-paintings-3827789">《Manic Street Preachers》在新单曲《People Ruin Paintings》中探索“真理的毁灭”，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="躁狂街传教士的詹姆斯·迪恩·布拉德菲尔德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_manicstreetpreachers_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/manic-street-preachers">Manic Street Preachers</a>分享了他们令人愉悦的新单曲“People Ruin Paintings”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-hiding-in-plain-sight-critical-thinking-art-interview-tour-3806178">Manic Street Preachers 分享苦乐参半的单曲“Hiding In Plain Sight”并宣布新专辑“Critical Thinking”</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌曲是继之前的单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-manic-street-preachers-triumphant-new-single-decline-fall-3788823">Decline &amp; Fall</a> ”和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/NICK-WIRE">Nicky Wire</a>主打的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-hiding-in-plain-sight-critical-thinking-art-interview-tour-3806178">“Hiding In Plain Sight”</a>之后的歌曲，取自他们即将发行的新专辑“Critical Thinking”。</p><p>与前一首非常相似，新单曲是一首激动人心的宽银幕赞歌，主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-dean-bradfield">詹姆斯·迪恩·布拉德菲尔德</a>在唱道中探讨了“真理的毁灭”：“<em>人们毁掉了画作，面孔只为了风景/人们毁掉了真理</em>。”你可以在下面听一下。</p><p> 《批判性思维》将于 1 月 31 日发行，它被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-hiding-in-plain-sight-critical-thinking-art-interview-tour-3806178">描述为“对立冲突的记录——试图找到解决路径的辩证法”</a> 。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="躁狂街传教士 - 人们毁灭绘画（官方视觉效果）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/V9VfV9pk9No?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “虽然音乐充满活力和哀伤的振奋，但大多数歌词都涉及对自我的冷酷分析，例外的是詹姆斯（主唱迪恩·布拉德菲尔德）的三首歌词，它们寻找并希望在人们、他们的生活中找到答案。记忆、语言和信仰，”Wire 最近告诉<em>NME</em> 。</p><p> “音乐充满活力，有时令人愉悦。录音有时可能是零星的和孤立的，有时我们在乐队环境中现场演奏，这又是彼此对立的。这些歌曲的核心存在着危机。它们是怀疑主义和怀疑的缩影，内在的驱动力似乎是不可避免的——从你自己开始，也许其余的都会随之而来。</p><p>布拉德菲尔德<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-on-new-album-critical-thinking-sometimes-just-to-have-your-best-songs-is-enough-3803752">之前解释过这张专辑背后几乎没有什么概念，只是它收录了“他们最好的一些歌曲</a>”。</p><p> “我们开始时比平时更加​​紧迫。在不知不觉中，我们已经进行了五六个演示……也许这是新冠疫情之后时间所剩无几的潜意识威胁，”他告诉<a href="https://www.mojo4music.com/articles/stories/manic-street-preachers-new-album-exclusive/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>MOJO</em></a> 。</p><p> “没有 MO。有时我们在一个特定的乐队环境中一起现场演奏，其他时候则更加孤立，我只是将吉他放在咔嗒声[轨道]上，或者尼克[Wire]用咔嗒声放下人声，或者我会这样做一个非常粗糙的声学版本，我们将以此为基础进行构建。所以这是大约两年的紧张、漫不经心的工作。”</p><p>他补充道：“有时仅仅拥有最好的歌曲就足够了，只需发行一张唱片，而不是试图描述一个大的总体概念，即使那里有一条线索。我们想要唱歌、玩耍、自由，并为尼克所写的歌词找到一个发光的地方。</p><p> “尼克试图分析他在世界上的地位，并调和他对现代政治或信仰的对抗——他的歌曲《批判性思维》谈论同理心和福利产业，而我们则陶醉于他人的破坏。我的三首歌以更务实的方式乐观地寻找答案。我有一首歌叫“受洗”，这是一张来自过去的明信片，讲述的是我和艾伦·图森特度过的美好的一天，沐浴在他的智慧、判断力和才华中。这就是他们的二分法。” </p><figure id="attachment_3806180" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3806180" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-3806180 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/manic_street_preachers_critical_thinking.jpg" alt="Manic Street Preachers 宣布推出第 15 张专辑“Critical Thinking”。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/manic_street_preachers_critical_thinking.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/manic_street_preachers_critical_thinking-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/manic_street_preachers_critical_thinking-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/manic_street_preachers_critical_thinking-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/manic_street_preachers_critical_thinking-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/manic_street_preachers_critical_thinking-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/manic_street_preachers_critical_thinking-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3806180" class="wp-caption-text"> Manic Street Preachers 宣布推出第 15 张专辑“Critical Thinking”。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>在讨论专辑艺术作品时，Wire 此前还告诉<em>NME</em> ：“我一直是大卫·赫恩的粉丝，他是现代纪实摄影的巨人。</p><p> “我买了几幅他漂亮的版画，长话短说，他最终来到了卡利恩的 Manics Door to the River 工作室，亲手交付了这些版画。我们整个早上都坐着聊天，故事令人着迷，咖啡很浓，时间过得很快。我见到大卫时他已经 89 岁了，他的热情和追求工作/艺术的意愿确实引起了我的共鸣，并推动我们不断前进。这最终导致了新的 Manics 唱片的封面——这张照片似乎表达了贯穿唱片本身的同样永恒的不确定性、怀疑和渴望。”</p><p> Wire 补充道：“Manics 唱片上收录了他的一张照片，真是令人激动不已，在我们发行第 15 张录音室专辑时，我们作为一支乐队，就像一面挽歌般的宽银幕渴望镜子。”</p><p>回顾他们的遗产，Wire <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/manic-street-preachers-ultra-vivid-lament-nicky-wire-james-dean-bradfield-3020202">之前还告诉<em>NME</em></a> ：“当你们在一起这么久并且彼此了解这么多时，更多地是通过本能进行沟通并发现制作歌曲的自然方式。我们三个人在遗忘中交谈过。我无法用其他方式来描述它。”</p><p>乐队将于四月份在英国举行一系列演出。您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fmanic-street-preachers-tickets%2Fartist%2F741429" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买剩余的门票。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-explore-destruction-of-truth-on-new-single-people-ruin-paintings-3827789">《Manic Street Preachers》在新单曲《People Ruin Paintings》中探索“真理的毁灭”，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
